**Line plotting**

We begin by simply plotting a straight line, you many choose any line of your choice. Generate your own data! (atleast 100 datapoints)

import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

# Generate data (100 datapoints)
x = np.linspace(0, 10, 100)
y = 2 * x + 5

#PLOT
plt.plot(x, y)
plt.xlabel("X values")
plt.ylabel("Y values")
plt.title("Straight Line Plot: y = 2x + 5")

plt.show()


